{"tid":2070652,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"紅底Facebook 刪除侵侵競選廣告","createTime":"2020-06-19T09:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T10:39:43.000Z","uid":143343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3a89a927f6e996855ace1ae1446d72f2113964a9","tid":2070652,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:17:59.000Z","msg":"美國大選將於年底舉行，特朗普尋求連任的競選工作也進行得如火如荼。然而，民權領袖、民主黨人以及 Facebook 員工認為特朗普部份競選廣告內容帶有仇恨及暴力意識，在多方施壓下，Facebook 於美國時間周四 (18/6) 決定刪除相關違反政策的廣告。<br />\n<br />\n被刪的廣告內容為一個黑框倒紅三角形，並寫上「極左暴徒正在街上到處引起動亂。他們正在摧毀我們的城市以及騷亂 &mdash; 完全是瘋狂的做法。請立即聯署支持總統及其決定將 ANTIFA 定義為恐怖組織。」黑框倒紅三角形在第二次世界大戰期間，被納粹德軍用於辨識集中營內的政治犯&hellip;"},{"pid":"97c46e6d138ea0989f7756473c1f5ddb5e767018","tid":2070652,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E7%AB%B6%E9%81%B8%E5%BB%A3%E5%91%8A%E9%A1%AF%E7%A4%BA%E7%B4%8D%E7%B2%B9%E9%9B%86%E4%B8%AD%E7%87%9F%E7%AC%A6%E8%99%9F-%E9%81%AD-facebook-%E5%88%AA%E9%99%A4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B2%25B9%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2587%259F%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E8%2599%259F-%25E9%2581%25AD-facebook-%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%2599%25A4%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84CycuUNiPSPuqsSoNSJcc%2FI4%3D&h=a9bddb9f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E7%25AB%25B6%25E9%2581%25B8%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E5%2591%258A%25E9%25A1%25AF%25E7%25A4%25BA%25E7%25B4%258D%25E7%25B2%25B9%25E9%259B%2586%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%2587%259F%25E7%25AC%25A6%25E8%2599%259F-%25E9%2581%25AD-facebook-%25E5%2588%25AA%25E9%2599%25A4%2F&h=87e0dda5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/inte